OL,7,FHopes of resolving the Birmingham bins
OL,8,Fdispute have taken a hit after Unite
OL,9,Fsaid lorry drivers' pay is to be cut.
OL,11,FMembers of the union have been on all-
OL,12,Fout strike since March, leading to
OL,13,Frubbish piling up on the streets, and
OL,14,Frats comfortably scurrying around in
OL,15,Fthe city.
OL,17,FTalks involving the conciliation
OL,18,Fservice Acas are to be held on
OL,19,FThursday after Unite said a deal could
OL,20,Fbe "within touching distance".
