OL,7,FBut, eight weeks into the strikes, the
OL,8,Funion has said Birmingham City Council
OL,9,Fhad decided to cut the pay of drivers,
OL,10,Fwarning it was an escalation of the
OL,11,Fdispute.
OL,13,FUnite said the council's proposed
OL,14,Fplans would mean, the pay rate of
OL,15,Fdrivers will reduce from #40,000 to
OL,16,F#32,000, a pay cut of #8,000.
OL,18,FIn a statement, Unite's general
OL,19,Fsecretary Sharon Graham said: "Today's
OL,20,Factions show clearly that Unite has
OL,21,Fbeen correct all along.
