OL,7,F"Birmingham City Council is taking
OL,8,Fmoney off workers to pay off their
OL,9,Fdebt to the Government.
OL,11,F"Workers are again paying the price
OL,12,Ffor bad decision after bad decision.
OL,14,F"Unite will not stand by and allow the
OL,15,Fcouncil and this Labour government to
OL,16,Finflict these savage pay cuts on
OL,17,Fworkers.
OL,19,F"It is completely unjustified and a
OL,20,Fclear escalation of the dispute.
