OL,7,F"It will not be accepted.
OL,9,F"No worker should be expected to lose
OL,10,Fthese eye-watering amounts of money
OL,11,Ffrom their pay packet.
OL,13,F"The Government has protected a Labour
OL,14,Fcouncil that has been treating workers
OL,15,Fin this outrageous way.
OL,17,F"It is no wonder Labour is
OL,18,Fincreasingly not seen as the party of
OL,19,Fworkers.
