OL,11,FCouncil said: "This fair and
OL,12,Ftransparent job evaluation process,
OL,13,Fjointly agreed with trade unions, is
OL,14,Fnecessary to ensure the council
OL,15,Fcomplies with equal pay laws.
OL,17,F"Today was the final workshop on the
OL,18,Fdriver team leader's role involving
